
1. set debug point by double click 
2. click on "debug" button (at the top to go Java code debug mode)
3. click "switch" button to open "Debug prespective"

Step Over
---------------------------
line by line execute

Step into
---------------------------
to execute particular function 

Step return
---------------------------
to back main execute point

Terminate "red button"
---------------------------
To stop debuging

click on  "java" 
---------------------------
Java coding mode

